Usage
Register and Login
Register on the app by providing a username, password, and the role (ROLE_USER). After registration, you can log in to the app.
Login with your credentials. Once authenticated, you will be able to manage your virtual pets.
Pets
Once logged in, you can choose your virtual pet and customize it. Available options:

Name: The name of your pet.
Color: Choose the color of the pet.
Action: You can choose from the available actions:
Train: Train your pet to improve its combat level.
Eat: Feed your pet to reduce its hunger level.
Sleep: Let your pet sleep to recover its energy.

Ready to Fight Dark Lord
Once your pet has been trained enough, it will be marked as Ready to Fight Dark Lord, allowing it to participate in special battles against the Dark Lord.


